{"tid":991378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90秒驚險畫面曝！他遭上司「噴槍捅屁股」灌風...一秒癱軟慘死","createTime":"2019-01-22T10:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:10:08.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7f60162ce12b654976268b09a9f46db5d02224","tid":991378,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S_lgFE1EO4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS_lgFE1EO4g&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=6fa2c511\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S_lgFE1EO4g</a><br />\n▲&nbsp;事發當下的90秒監視器畫面曝光。（影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n全球「噴槍殺人」案件其實曾發生過許多次，而上一起令人震驚的個案就發生在印度。去年9月，馬哈拉施特拉邦（Maharashtra）一間鑄造廠的主管沃格摩爾（Rakesh Wagmore）和員工賈達（ditya Jadhav）開玩笑惡作劇，拿起空氣壓縮噴槍狠插下屬肛門，導致他當場腿軟倒地不起、腸道嚴重受損，經搶救15天仍不幸身亡。<br />\n根據90秒的監視器畫面，當時身在工廠的賈達上前與沃格摩爾對話，沃格摩爾手拿噴槍和賈達玩了起來，先對著賈達的頭髮、衣服、背部、頸部噴了之後，突然間把噴槍口對準賈達的肛門惡作劇，不料賈達無法承受這突如其來的刺激，隨即腿軟倒地不起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3853/d3853021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3853%2Fd3853021.jpg&h=8c572f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 主管突然把空氣壓縮噴槍往下屬肛門插去。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Abanoub Samy）<br />\n事發後，賈達被緊急送往醫院治療，經醫師評估，他的腸道嚴重受損。在與死神奮鬥15天後，他於2018年9月18日不治身亡。而肇事者沃格摩爾在闖下大禍後，立即神隱躲避責任，遭到警方起訴並追查。<br />\n影片曝光後，網友紛紛留言表示，「這上司是多麼的愚蠢」、「這種智商怎麼當上主管的？」、「用想的就覺得好痛......」。<br />\n同樣情節去年也在日本埼玉縣一間工廠上演，當時一名員工被2名同事拿空氣噴槍「灌腸」傷重不治，闖下大禍的2人則被當局依據傷害致死罪逮捕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190122/1362948.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190122%2F1362948.htm&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=a0bd68ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190122/1362948.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f8d5e8f350fb51b2f8af5e6c297b2a261328960","tid":991378,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1033b9968913280e08b8a13ba4c1ca8c41dc964a","tid":991378,"uid":211887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"Old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079df7ae01714e3174dd4f0ff626e74a16ee17b6","tid":991378,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"D基佬最想要既野黎"},{"pid":"24f4ff2036f18416108ff4d8113c7224250f6dcd","tid":991378,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"印度男嘅窿洞情義結，比港男厲害廿倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10993b9415fd79af8087699ef11933d65ca18192","tid":991378,"uid":61545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"立即神隱躲避責任<br />\n睇到呢句唔知點解笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc9c3ff9c11c30a2cafe44778a75e108971ce7d","tid":991378,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cb9106e6b5cd5ec7e6a2f9ba6148374069c86e7","tid":991378,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d35d9cce59e83b6f6a0401ca6588f056c12005c9","tid":991378,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"一下就瓜左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c1162795e6d475872c9b6ff9f6b020477803bc","tid":991378,"uid":35547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"連登咁多gay佬 可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}